name: Playground
description: A demonstration application developed based on Dataverse SDK

streams.schema:
type playground_indexFolders @createModel(accountRelation: LIST, description: "Dataverse:playground | IndexFolder") {
  author: DID! @documentAccount
  version: CommitID! @documentVersion
  appVersion: String! @string(maxLength: 100)
  folderType: Int!
  contentFolderIds: [String!]! @list(minLength: 1, maxLength: 10000) @string(maxLength: 2000)
  createdAt: DateTime!
  updatedAt: DateTime!
  options: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  parentFolderId: String @string(maxLength: 1000)
  childFolderIds: [String] @list(maxLength: 10000) @string(maxLength: 2000)
  deleted: Boolean
}

type playground_indexFiles @createModel(accountRelation: LIST, description: "Dataverse:playground | IndexFile") {
  author: DID! @documentAccount
  version: CommitID! @documentVersion
  appVersion: String! @string(maxLength: 100)
  contentId: String! @string(maxLength: 1000)
  contentType: String! @string(maxLength: 100)
  comment: String! @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  relation: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  additional: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  datatokenId: String @string(maxLength: 1000)
  fileType: Int!
  encryptedSymmetricKey: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  decryptionConditions: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  decryptionConditionsType: String @string(maxLength: 100)
  createdAt: DateTime!
  updatedAt: DateTime!
  deleted: Boolean
}

type playground_post @createModel(accountRelation: LIST, description: "Dataverse:playground | PlaygroundPost_test3") {
  author: DID! @documentAccount
  version: CommitID! @documentVersion
  appVersion: String! @string(maxLength: 100)
  text: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  images: [String] @list(maxLength: 10000000) @string(maxLength: 2000000)
  videos: [String] @list(maxLength: 10000000) @string(maxLength: 2000000)
  options: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  createdAt: DateTime!
  updatedAt: DateTime!
  encrypted: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
}
